divs: sighting details@ approx 6:00 pm tonight (est), i was sitting on my parents couch looking out the huge picture window they have in the living room, the window faces roughly west-north\west, i saw a bright white light traverse from south to north at a high altitude and at tremendous speed. it did not appear to be a shooting star as there was no tell tale trail of debris falling off, there was no tail at all. just a bright white light travelling really, really fast
Summary: saw a really fast moving starlike sphere traverse sky in a south to north direction at high altitude
